{"parse":{"title":"Raw Bristle Whisker Catfish","pageid":63420,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|c=2}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_30\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=6308\n|ilvl=25\n|name=Raw Bristle Whisker Catfish\n|level=15\n|charges=1\n|stack=20\n|effect=Use: Restores 243 health over 21 sec.  Must remain seated while eating.}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Source==\n\nThe most reliable way to attain this item is by [[Fishing locations|fishing]] however it can also be looted randomly from some level 18-44 [[Beast]] and [[Humanoid]] monsters.\n\n==Raw Bristle Whisker Catfish as an ingredient==\nThis item is used to make: \n* {{loot|Common|Bristle Whisker Catfish}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|6308}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/raw_bristle_whisker_catfish.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common items]]"}}}